In order to accomplish these objects, a washer comprises a body having a water tub in a vertical shaft; a door for covering an opening of the water tub and providing a foldable second hinge member and a first hinge member hingable to the body; a door close/open apparatus for closing or opening the opening with the door by forward or reverse rotation of a motor.